==English==

===Verb===
'''housebreaking'''

Present participle of '''housebreak'''.

# To break into another's house with unlawful intent.
# The accused was caught housebreaking into Mr Smith's home.


===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The act of breaking into another person's house with unlawful intent. Housebreaking is a criminal offence.
#: ''The [[accused]] was charged with '''housebreaking''' and theft.''

